Hoobot

   Access h2g2 automatically!

For installation details, see INSTALL (which doesn't exist, try following
perlmodinstall for now).

For usage, see the doco. Either use perldoc or view it
on the web at:
    <http://search.cpan.org/author/BSMITH/Hoobot/>

Changes for 0.5.0 (26 July 2003)
  - Initial release
  - Fifth generation of the Hoobot idea, but a totally new code style!

This module may eventually become WWW::H2G2.

For a complete list of changes, see the Changes file (when it's written).


by Benjamin Smith.
